b4e94fcd0e991ebc0","tid":2079624,"uid":47208,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42ef9e3fbf800a0526964563ac8a5a957accab41","tid":2079624,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/564234/f/800x0/https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200623/share_2020062309163513439.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F564234%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200623%2Fshare_2020062309163513439.jpg&h=2e99a995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一單個細節 我印像中好似冇人POST過<br />\n睇內文,大家就會知 事實上外國資金入黎支持暴亂<br />\n並不只我地明面睇到肥老黎資金 而他的資金只是冰山一角<br />\n大家諗諗 只係其中一個ACC 都已經輕易洗到3.6億黑金<br />\n所以亂港黑金規模極可以達數十億元！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一方面我地要屌既係 銀行監管到係咪有咩問題出現左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文中RAYMOND講到明係發紗銀行戶口 而香港就只有三間<br />\n佢洗錢時講到明比黑暴用 咁基本上可以排除佢地會用中銀<br />\n咁結果即係洗錢活動集中在二家英資銀行 - 渣打同匯豐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呵呵 唔怪得阿爺郁尻渣打同匯豐啦<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n近期有人在社交網站發布「搵快錢」廣告，有市民和本報記者查詢時獲悉，對方自稱是援助示威者基金負責人，稱只要借出網上銀行帳號，讓美國慈善機構匯款至帳戶，每月即可賺取逾萬元。《星島日報》報道，消息稱，警方正調查是否有不法之徒藉詞「支持手足」借他人帳戶「漂白」非法資金。警方指去年涉及懷疑「洗黑錢」的可疑交易報告逾五萬宗，呼籲市民對聲稱能賺快錢的途徑加以警惕，以免誤墮法網。記者：陶法德<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">市民陳先生早前從網上看到一則招聘廣告，內容稱「搵錢攻略抗疫又搵錢，善用時間賺取幾千至幾萬不等」，於是通過手機社交程式聯絡，自稱Raymond男子聲稱是「幫助黃絲帶的資金籌集會」工作人員，表示只要提供銀行帳戶，用作協助基金存取款項，即可輕鬆賺錢。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1802413/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E8%87%AA%E7%A8%B1-%E6%92%90%E6%89%8B%E8%B6%B3%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E7%96%91%E6%B6%89%E6%B4%97%E9%8C%A2-%E6%9C%88%E8%B3%BA%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%8B%9B%E5%BE%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1802413%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E6%2592%2590%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591-%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%25B4%2597%25E9%258C%25A2-%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%25BE%25A0&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=67bec0ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1802413%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E6%2592%2590%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591-%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%25B4%2597%25E9%258C%25A2-%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%25BE%25A0&h=502d6292\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1802413/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E8%87%AA%E7%A8%B1-%E6%92%90%E6%89%8B%E8%B6%B3%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E7%96%91%E6%B6%89%E6%B4%97%E9%8C%A2-%E6%9C%88%E8%B3%BA%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%8B%9B%E5%BE%A0</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:14:52.000Z","msg":"引用<br />\n「文中RAYMOND講到明係發紗銀行戶口 而香港就只有三間<br />\n佢洗錢時講到明比<span style=\"color: orange;\">黑暴</span>用 咁基本上可以排除佢地會用中銀」<br />\n<br />\n如果你係有腦既香港人/ 連登仔<br />\n我諗唔到點解會用<span style=\"color: orange;\">黑暴</span>呢個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係新聞內容都話<br />\n係你自己打嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<